Of course,

274
00:16:15,800 --> 00:16:16,760
if it is possible.

275
00:16:19,800 --> 00:16:21,800
[dramatic music]

276
00:16:34,840 --> 00:16:36,120
I promise you.

277
00:16:36,720 --> 00:16:38,120
I will keep your secret.

278
00:16:39,240 --> 00:16:41,280
But they will know this sooner or later.

279
00:16:42,640 --> 00:16:43,960
This is not a long-term solution.

280
00:16:45,400 --> 00:16:46,520
Zhuo Zhi,

281
00:16:47,560 --> 00:16:48,640
You asked me

282
00:16:48,920 --> 00:16:50,120
why I fight so hard.

283
00:16:51,960 --> 00:16:54,680
I think I won't have many
more opportunities

284
00:16:54,800 --> 00:16:56,880
to play tennis with you all

285
00:16:57,680 --> 00:16:58,720
in the future.

286
00:16:59,560 --> 00:17:01,680
So, I will strive for it

287
00:17:01,760 --> 00:17:03,920
with the strength that I have.

288
00:17:04,480 --> 00:17:06,079
This should be fun, right?

289
00:17:09,880 --> 00:17:11,560
I just didn't expect you
to strive so hard.

290
00:17:12,160 --> 00:17:14,800
[breathes heavily]

291
00:17:20,880 --> 00:17:22,160
[Siyang] I always think

292
00:17:23,000 --> 00:17:24,599
you understand me the most.

293
00:17:27,960 --> 00:17:29,560
In fact, we are the same. Right?

294
00:17:32,319 --> 00:17:33,160
I almost forgot.

295
00:17:34,520 --> 00:17:35,520
Let's run as a punishment.

296
00:17:37,440 --> 00:17:38,400
Why?

297
00:17:38,960 --> 00:17:41,760
People who have competitions
in private will be punished.

298
00:17:42,120 --> 00:17:43,400
Let's run 50 laps.

299
00:17:44,560 --> 00:17:45,840
[soft chuckle]

300
00:17:46,440 --> 00:17:47,680
[indistinct chatter]

301
00:17:47,760 --> 00:17:51,200
TWO DAYS TO GO BEFORE THE MATCH BETWEEN
YU QING AND XING YAO

302
00:17:54,880 --> 00:17:56,880
[comical music]

303
00:17:59,720 --> 00:18:01,040
Let me drink your water.

304
00:18:12,480 --> 00:18:14,920
[gulps]

305
00:18:20,560 --> 00:18:21,520
Hm.

306
00:18:34,320 --> 00:18:36,040
[Ying pants, gasps]

307
00:18:36,120 --> 00:18:37,760
[Ying] Sorry.

308
00:18:38,320 --> 00:18:39,600
That is Ying.

309
00:18:41,240 --> 00:18:42,600
She dropped something.

310
00:18:42,680 --> 00:18:43,720
Let's go and have a look.

311
00:18:49,720 --> 00:18:51,360
The key to Yu Qing Tennis Court.

312
00:18:51,440 --> 00:18:53,120
Why is it in Ying's hand?

313
00:18:53,200 --> 00:18:54,440
[pants]

314
00:18:54,560 --> 00:18:56,600
Luckily, I haven't lost it. Thank you.

315
00:18:56,800 --> 00:18:57,960
[soft chuckle]

316
00:18:58,160 --> 00:18:59,360
You are here at the right time.

317
00:18:59,760 --> 00:19:01,840
How about having a meal with us together?

318
00:19:04,560 --> 00:19:05,480
Okay.

319
00:19:05,640 --> 00:19:08,120
I will be back after I return
the key to the court.

320
00:19:08,200 --> 00:19:09,080
Wait.

321
00:19:10,200 --> 00:19:12,520
Why is the key in your hand?

322
00:19:12,960 --> 00:19:14,280
Zhuo Zhi gave it to me.

323
00:19:15,520 --> 00:19:16,680
Zhuo Zhi?

324
00:19:17,120 --> 00:19:18,040
Yes.

325
00:19:18,120 --> 00:19:19,000
Hey.

326
00:19:19,160 --> 00:19:20,600
You seem to be unhappy.

327
00:19:21,400 --> 00:19:22,480
[gasps]

328
00:19:22,920 --> 00:19:23,760
[stutters]

329
00:19:24,320 --> 00:19:25,480
No, it is not what you think.

330
00:19:25,560 --> 00:19:27,160
I happened to meet Zhuo Zhi

331
00:19:27,240 --> 00:19:28,400
on my way here.

332
00:19:28,480 --> 00:19:30,640
He borrowed the keys yesterday
but forgot to return it.

333
00:19:30,720 --> 00:19:32,080
He asked me to return it for him.

334
00:19:32,160 --> 00:19:33,640
He didn't come to meet me on purpose.

335
00:19:34,200 --> 00:19:35,960
Yesterday after the training

336
00:19:36,640 --> 00:19:39,640
didn't Zhuo Zhi and Captain leave first?

337
00:19:40,560 --> 00:19:43,040
Why did they go back
and take the key to the court?

338
00:19:43,600 --> 00:19:46,440
Maybe they think they will
have a match with Xing Yao

339
00:19:47,000 --> 00:19:49,080
so they want to practice together.

340
00:19:50,640 --> 00:19:52,640
-[Qiao Chen] Oh.
-Then I will go and return the key.

341
00:19:58,320 --> 00:19:59,480
Training?

342
00:20:00,440 --> 00:20:02,240
Train at this time?

343
00:20:02,560 --> 00:20:04,160
With Captain?

344
00:20:04,440 --> 00:20:06,800
-Let's go training this afternoon.
-Lu Xia.

345
00:20:08,840 --> 00:20:10,600
Can you keep a secret?

346
00:20:10,760 --> 00:20:12,200
-Why?
-How about this?

347
00:20:13,040 --> 00:20:15,360
You tell me a secret
and I will keep it for you.

348
00:20:15,440 --> 00:20:17,720
I will tell you a secret
and you keep it for me.

349
00:20:18,280 --> 00:20:19,680
No, I don't want to.

350
00:20:20,080 --> 00:20:20,960
Hey.

351
00:20:22,160 --> 00:20:23,520
I really can't bear it.

352
00:20:23,600 --> 00:20:24,760
I am about to explode

353
00:20:24,840 --> 00:20:26,280
if I can't find someone to talk to.

354
00:20:26,360 --> 00:20:27,840
You can talk to Baiyang.

355
00:20:28,400 --> 00:20:29,400
No.

356
00:20:29,480 --> 00:20:31,240
The match with Xing Yao is about to start.

357
00:20:31,320 --> 00:20:33,320
They are the main players,
can't be influenced.

358
00:20:33,800 --> 00:20:34,960
Then you can find Huang Jing.

359
00:20:37,040 --> 00:20:38,080
I am telling you

360
00:20:38,160 --> 00:20:39,440
Captain's arm injury is serious.

361
00:20:39,520 --> 00:20:41,160
He is not suitable to play with Ji Jingwu.

362
00:20:41,520 --> 00:20:43,520
[ominous music]

363
00:20:49,120 --> 00:20:50,880
[phone ringing]

364
00:20:52,760 --> 00:20:53,720
Hello.

365
00:20:53,800 --> 00:20:54,760
[man 1] Miss Qi.

366
00:20:55,600 --> 00:20:57,360
Yes, sir.

367
00:20:57,720 --> 00:20:59,320
[man 1] Oh. I have good news.

368
00:20:59,800 --> 00:21:03,120
The application you sent for the
overseas learning chance has been relied.

369
00:21:03,200 --> 00:21:04,440
What does it say?

370
00:21:05,160 --> 00:21:08,200
[man 1] Mu Siyang has passed
the first check.

371
00:21:09,040 --> 00:21:10,440
As soon as he pass the final review,

372
00:21:10,520 --> 00:21:12,760
he can go abroad this month.

373
00:21:31,760 --> 00:21:35,360
Zhuo Zhi, I have something
to discuss with you.

374
00:21:35,440 --> 00:21:36,800
Did you play tennis with Captain

375
00:21:36,880 --> 00:21:38,280
after the training yesterday?

376
00:21:39,800 --> 00:21:41,080
[sighs]

377
00:21:41,560 --> 00:21:43,000
Didn't I tell you not to tell others?

378
00:21:43,920 --> 00:21:46,600
Zhuo Zhi, you know he hurt his arm,

379
00:21:47,000 --> 00:21:49,240
why do you still play
with him at this time?

380
00:21:49,680 --> 00:21:50,800
Did the captain win?

381
00:21:53,680 --> 00:21:54,760
Why do you ask this?

382
00:21:54,840 --> 00:21:57,320
If there is nothing wrong with his arm,
he definitely won't lose.

383
00:22:00,120 --> 00:22:01,880
It is between Siyang and me.

384
00:22:02,040 --> 00:22:03,120
I don't have to tell you.

385
00:22:04,560 --> 00:22:05,680
As for the his injury,

386
00:22:08,080 --> 00:22:09,440
you don't have to worry about it.

387
00:22:10,040 --> 00:22:11,240
Really?

388
00:22:13,080 --> 00:22:15,720
He will be playing for
the match with Xing Yao.

389
00:22:17,680 --> 00:22:18,920
Great.

390
00:22:19,000 --> 00:22:20,720
Zhuo Zhi, look at you.

391
00:22:20,800 --> 00:22:23,200
Why not tell me earlier that he is okay?

392
00:22:23,280 --> 00:22:25,560
-[Qiao Chen] I can't even eat these days.
-Okay, I am going.

393
00:22:27,800 --> 00:22:28,720
Eh. Lu Xia.

394
00:22:31,400 --> 00:22:32,320
[sighs]

395
00:22:34,600 --> 00:22:36,160
[Qiao Chen] Lu Xia, wait a minute.

396
00:22:36,840 --> 00:22:38,920
-You mean--
-Think about it.

397
00:22:39,840 --> 00:22:41,960
[Lu Xia] Zhuo Zhi said we don't have
to worry about it,

398
00:22:42,040 --> 00:22:44,240
but he didn't say Captain's arm is okay.

399
00:22:44,480 --> 00:22:46,040
[coins jangling]

400
00:22:46,160 --> 00:22:47,360
[Qiao Chen] Captain's hand...

401
00:22:48,200 --> 00:22:49,240
No.

402
00:22:49,320 --> 00:22:50,400
I can't bear it.

403
00:22:50,840 --> 00:22:52,880
This thing should be known by more people.

404
00:22:52,960 --> 00:22:55,920
I think it is better not to tell them
considering the situation now.

405
00:23:01,160 --> 00:23:04,120
MUNICH TENNIS COLLEGE

406
00:23:04,680 --> 00:23:05,600
[Siyang] Coach.

407
00:23:05,920 --> 00:23:07,240
I know what you are going to say.

408
00:23:07,320 --> 00:23:08,480
[Coach Qi] Listen to me first.

409
00:23:09,240 --> 00:23:11,320
The country has spent a lot of
money and energy

410
00:23:11,400 --> 00:23:13,040
fostering the future tennis players.

411
00:23:13,760 --> 00:23:14,840
The sports committee

412
00:23:14,920 --> 00:23:16,200
has backup of your material.

413
00:23:16,920 --> 00:23:18,280
The national tennis training center

414
00:23:18,600 --> 00:23:20,520
has found the best doctors

415
00:23:20,680 --> 00:23:22,040
to treat your arm

416
00:23:22,320 --> 00:23:23,400
overseas.

417
00:23:24,440 --> 00:23:25,640
This time, if you go,

418
00:23:26,080 --> 00:23:28,600
your arm will completely recover.

419
00:23:29,640 --> 00:23:30,920
Everyone has been expecting

420
00:23:31,000 --> 00:23:32,080
the match for a year.

421
00:23:32,560 --> 00:23:33,880
Your arm injury

422
00:23:34,200 --> 00:23:35,440
cannot be delayed anymore.

423
00:23:36,680 --> 00:23:37,600
Coach.

424
00:23:39,120 --> 00:23:41,920
I know you and the sports committee
have done a lot for me.

425
00:23:42,200 --> 00:23:43,200
I am clear that

426
00:23:44,080 --> 00:23:46,320
this opportunity is everyone's dream.

427
00:23:47,200 --> 00:23:48,640
-But--
-But

428
00:23:49,040 --> 00:23:50,080
you should be clear that

429
00:23:50,560 --> 00:23:51,680
even if you are not here,

430
00:23:51,760 --> 00:23:54,360
they will try their best to compete.

431
00:23:54,640 --> 00:23:56,280
It is a promise between
team members and me

432
00:23:56,360 --> 00:23:58,360
that we will enter
the national tournament together.

433
00:23:58,440 --> 00:23:59,640
It is also my belief.

434
00:24:00,600 --> 00:24:02,200
I don't want to give up like this.

435
00:24:02,760 --> 00:24:05,360
Even if the price is you can't
play tennis anymore?

436
00:24:06,320 --> 00:24:07,680
[exhales sharply]

437
00:24:09,640 --> 00:24:11,360
Qiao Chen, you are unbelievable.

438
00:24:11,600 --> 00:24:13,240
You didn't even tell us about the matter.

439
00:24:13,800 --> 00:24:15,960
[Qiao Chen] We are about to have a match
with Xing Yao

440
00:24:16,520 --> 00:24:17,960
I don't want to influence your mood.

441
00:24:18,560 --> 00:24:19,520
[Dayong] Don't worry.

442
00:24:19,680 --> 00:24:21,160
Let's confirm it with the coach first.

443
00:24:21,280 --> 00:24:23,920
Last time when I accompanied Captain
for the further consultation--

444
00:24:24,000 --> 00:24:25,520
What? You already knew a long time ago?

445
00:24:26,360 --> 00:24:27,960
The doctor said it was okay at that time.

446
00:24:28,080 --> 00:24:30,320
And Captain looks normal when training.

447
00:24:30,400 --> 00:24:31,400
So...

448
00:24:31,480 --> 00:24:33,760
[Tang Jiale] You may not tell them,

449
00:24:33,840 --> 00:24:34,960
but how can you not tell me?

450
00:24:41,080 --> 00:24:42,280
[sighs]

451
00:24:43,320 --> 00:24:45,520
[Coach Qi] This is the material about
the German hospital.

452
00:24:45,680 --> 00:24:46,840
You can have a look.

453
00:24:47,840 --> 00:24:49,400
You are more aware than

454
00:24:49,480 --> 00:24:51,440
anyone else about your injury.

455
00:24:52,320 --> 00:24:54,200
-[sighs]
-[Coach Qi] The most important thing now

456
00:24:54,280 --> 00:24:55,680
is not about the promise you made.

457
00:24:55,760 --> 00:24:57,240
It is whether you can

458
00:24:57,320 --> 00:24:58,920
play in the future.

459
00:24:59,680 --> 00:25:01,680
[somber music]

460
00:25:20,000 --> 00:25:21,360
You all...

461
00:25:21,440 --> 00:25:22,600
finished training?

462
00:25:23,200 --> 00:25:24,920
Everyone knows about

463
00:25:25,000 --> 00:25:26,360
Captain's arm injury.

464
00:25:27,400 --> 00:25:28,280
Oh.

465
00:25:28,520 --> 00:25:29,440
Is that so?

466
00:25:29,720 --> 00:25:30,880
Not just like this.

467
00:25:30,960 --> 00:25:33,080
[Qiao Chen] We wanted to confirm
with the coach.

468
00:25:33,160 --> 00:25:35,520
But we heard the coach tell Captain that

469
00:25:35,600 --> 00:25:38,320
the school wants him to train
and treat his hand abroad.

470
00:25:40,240 --> 00:25:42,360
Isn't it captain's purpose

471
00:25:42,880 --> 00:25:44,800
to lead Yu Qing to enter National League?

472
00:25:44,880 --> 00:25:47,160
Everyone is clear about
Ji Jingwu's strength.

473
00:25:47,760 --> 00:25:49,000
If captain plays with him

474
00:25:50,000 --> 00:25:51,200
then his arm...

475
00:25:52,000 --> 00:25:53,520
Even if the captain won't play

476
00:25:53,600 --> 00:25:55,160
we are not bound to lose right?

477
00:26:01,280 --> 00:26:03,920
YU QING XING YAO

478
00:26:04,560 --> 00:26:05,720
If the captain is not here,

479
00:26:06,240 --> 00:26:08,160
the chances that we defeat Xing Yao is...

480
00:26:08,400 --> 00:26:10,680
[gasps]
What are you doing?

481
00:26:10,760 --> 00:26:12,360
What do you expect to see?

482
00:26:12,600 --> 00:26:14,760
If the captain is not here
and we can't defeat Xing Yao,

483
00:26:14,840 --> 00:26:15,880
will you quit the match?

484
00:26:16,480 --> 00:26:17,600
We can ask the captain

485
00:26:17,680 --> 00:26:19,480
if we should play or not.

486
00:26:20,240 --> 00:26:21,160
I agree.

487
00:26:21,960 --> 00:26:23,960
Why not ask Siyang?

488
00:26:24,360 --> 00:26:25,600
After all,

489
00:26:25,680 --> 00:26:27,680
none of us can decide his life for him.

490
00:26:28,520 --> 00:26:29,360
Isn't it?

491
00:26:43,920 --> 00:26:47,080
Captain, we just heard that
your left arm--

492
00:26:47,160 --> 00:26:49,760
What is the punishment for being late
for training without a reason?

493
00:26:50,640 --> 00:26:51,640
Twenty laps.

494
00:26:52,360 --> 00:26:55,480
But we heard that the school
wants you to go abroad--

495
00:26:55,560 --> 00:26:56,760
Do you want to find excuses

496
00:26:56,960 --> 00:26:58,280
to avoid punishment?

497
00:26:59,960 --> 00:27:01,040
Okay.

498
00:27:01,120 --> 00:27:02,600
We have already delayed the training.

499
00:27:03,160 --> 00:27:04,320
As for the punishment,

500
00:27:04,400 --> 00:27:06,560
we can carry it out after the training.

501
00:27:07,560 --> 00:27:08,800
Everyone start training!

502
00:27:14,080 --> 00:27:16,240
-[exhales heavily]
-[sighs]

503
00:27:27,080 --> 00:27:29,680
-[thumping]
-[thwacking]

504
00:27:31,120 --> 00:27:32,400
[whooshes]

505
00:27:35,400 --> 00:27:37,400
[light music]

506
00:27:52,640 --> 00:27:54,160
[whooshes]

507
00:28:06,680 --> 00:28:09,120
[both grunting]

508
00:28:11,440 --> 00:28:13,400
[pants]

509
00:28:28,120 --> 00:28:29,080
Captain.

510
00:28:33,080 --> 00:28:34,280
[Qiao Chen] Go and ask him.

511
00:28:35,280 --> 00:28:36,200
Go and ask him.

512
00:28:37,760 --> 00:28:38,960
Ask him.

513
00:28:39,440 --> 00:28:40,920
-Me?
-[Qiao Chen] Ask him.

514
00:28:41,480 --> 00:28:42,760
Why not you ask him?

515
00:28:43,600 --> 00:28:44,600
You should ask him.

516
00:28:44,960 --> 00:28:46,280
[sighs]
Okay.

517
00:28:46,400 --> 00:28:47,840
I know what you want to say.

518
00:28:50,600 --> 00:28:51,760
Tidy up the court,

519
00:28:51,840 --> 00:28:53,360
then we will have a marathon training

520
00:28:53,440 --> 00:28:55,200
outside the school.

521
00:29:06,520 --> 00:29:08,880
[all panting]

522
00:29:14,880 --> 00:29:15,920
Why?

523
00:29:17,280 --> 00:29:19,520
This is the place where we
played with Xing Yao last year.

524
00:29:20,760 --> 00:29:22,760
[dramatic music]

525
00:29:23,520 --> 00:29:24,640
[exhales deeply]

526
00:29:25,440 --> 00:29:26,280
Follow me.

527
00:29:27,840 --> 00:29:29,840
[dramatic music]

528
00:29:49,120 --> 00:29:51,120
[dramatic music continues]

529
00:30:06,680 --> 00:30:09,800
[crowd] Yu Qing!

530
00:30:09,880 --> 00:30:13,440
[crowd] Xing Yao!

531
00:30:21,160 --> 00:30:23,960
[crowd cheering]

532
00:30:31,000 --> 00:30:32,680
[puffing]

533
00:30:39,480 --> 00:30:41,520
[somber music]

534
00:30:55,600 --> 00:30:57,680
[somber music continues]

535
00:31:02,160 --> 00:31:04,520
NATIONAL SENIOR HIGH MALE TENNIS LEAGUE
PROVINCIAL COMPETITION

536
00:31:04,600 --> 00:31:06,960
JI JINGWU VERSUS MU SIYANG
ROUND SCORE 5 TO 7

537
00:31:09,680 --> 00:31:11,200
[clatters]

538
00:31:11,440 --> 00:31:13,000
[grunts]

539
00:31:22,520 --> 00:31:24,360
JI JINGWU VERSUS MU SIYANG
ROUND SCORE 5 TO 7

540
00:31:34,280 --> 00:31:36,560
[crowd] Xing Yao!

541
00:31:36,640 --> 00:31:37,880
Xing Yao!

542
00:31:38,000 --> 00:31:40,080
[crowd] Xing Yao!

543
00:31:43,440 --> 00:31:47,400
[crowd] Xing Yao!

544
00:32:05,760 --> 00:32:07,080
Last year, we stood here.

545
00:32:07,640 --> 00:32:08,640
Till now.

546
00:32:09,440 --> 00:32:10,840
we had been through a lot.

547
00:32:11,560 --> 00:32:13,040
I can still remember the moment

548
00:32:13,880 --> 00:32:14,960
when we lost last year.

549
00:32:16,120 --> 00:32:17,240
But if I think carefully,

550
00:32:17,720 --> 00:32:19,000
