551
00:32:19,600 --> 00:32:21,000
from the goal we set at that time.

552
00:32:21,080 --> 00:32:22,960
We are about to have another
match with Xing Yao.

553
00:32:24,840 --> 00:32:25,960
If we can take it,

554
00:32:26,720 --> 00:32:28,640
