the national league.

555
00:32:30,080 --> 00:32:31,240
The goal we set

556
00:32:31,640 --> 00:32:33,240
is never as close to us

557
00:32:33,680 --> 00:32:35,040
as it is now.

558
00:32:35,120 --> 00:32:36,400
Captain.

559
00:32:36,480 --> 00:32:37,560
In this year,

560
00:32:37,640 --> 00:32:39,440
we kept training and

561
00:32:39,520 --> 00:32:42,520
experienced a lot
to finally come to this far.

562
00:32:43,160 --> 00:32:44,520
So I won't leave you

563
00:32:44,920 --> 00:32:46,280
at this moment.

564
00:32:46,880 --> 00:32:49,440
For me, nothing is more important

565
00:32:49,520 --> 00:32:52,640
than entering the national
league with you all.

566
00:32:53,320 --> 00:32:55,480
But Captain, your arm...

567
00:32:55,560 --> 00:32:57,080
your arm...

568
00:32:57,320 --> 00:32:59,320
Can you play the next competitions
with it?

569
00:33:00,800 --> 00:33:02,080
Are you giving up tennis?

570
00:33:04,040 --> 00:33:05,320
You can convince me.

571
00:33:05,400 --> 00:33:06,480
