574
00:33:15,040 --> 00:33:16,240
[sighs]

575
00:33:16,760 --> 00:33:17,960
Don't worry, everyone.

576
00:33:18,040 --> 00:33:19,120
I will finish my competition

577
00:33:20,240 --> 00:33:22,280
with Ji Jingwu in 30 minutes.

578
00:33:22,840 --> 00:33:24,240
[Siyang] If I can't,

579
00:33:24,320 --> 00:33:25,320
I will give up.

580
00:33:25,880 --> 00:33:27,720
I will accept the result
and receive treatment.

581
00:33:28,560 --> 00:33:29,520
And

582
00:33:30,240 --> 00:33:32,120
I never thought of giving up.

583
00:33:34,000 --> 00:33:35,160
Anyway,

584
00:33:35,960 --> 00:33:38,280
