the national league together.

585
00:33:39,040 --> 00:33:40,560
[Siyang] I have never changed my will

586
00:33:40,640 --> 00:33:43,120
from beginning till now.

587
00:33:43,400 --> 00:33:44,640
So I invite everyone

588
00:33:44,720 --> 00:33:47,120
to keep the promise we have made

589
00:33:47,680 --> 00:33:49,920
and fight till the very end.

590
00:33:54,880 --> 00:33:55,880
Yu Qing.

591
00:34:00,000 --> 00:34:01,520
[all] Winner!

592
