593
00:34:18,159 --> 00:34:20,159
[theme music continues]

594
00:34:40,239 --> 00:34:42,280
We have the same idea.

595
00:34:43,000 --> 00:34:44,400
We must finish

596
00:34:45,600 --> 00:34:47,760
the competitions with Xing Yao

597
00:34:47,840 --> 00:34:48,960
before the Captain is on.

598
00:35:02,360 --> 00:35:04,480
[birds chirping]

599
00:35:06,000 --> 00:35:08,200
-[Baiyang] Yan.
-[Yan Zhiming] Hmm?

600
00:35:08,440 --> 00:35:09,800
Last time when we said we want

601
00:35:09,880 --> 00:35:11,960
to defeat Xing Yao before captain is on,

602
00:35:12,040 --> 00:35:13,200
you didn't say a word.

603
00:35:13,760 --> 00:35:14,720
Why?

604
00:35:15,040 --> 00:35:16,240
You must have done the math

605
00:35:16,680 --> 00:35:18,240
about the chances we can defeat Xing Yao

606
00:35:18,320 --> 00:35:19,560
before captain is on.

607
00:35:22,960 --> 00:35:26,600
Zhiming, your hand grip is worn out.

608
00:35:27,880 --> 00:35:29,800
I have a new one. Here you are.

609
00:35:31,120 --> 00:35:32,200
Thanks.

610
00:35:32,320 --> 00:35:34,680
But I have tested all kinds of hand grip.

611
00:35:35,240 --> 00:35:37,000
Only the one I use now

612
00:35:37,160 --> 00:35:39,160
can best help me perform steadily
in statistics.

613
00:35:39,760 --> 00:35:41,800
