if you try the new one.

614
00:35:43,000 --> 00:35:44,600
I still believe my data.

615
00:35:45,440 --> 00:35:46,280
[scoffs]

616
00:35:46,360 --> 00:35:47,200
You are stubborn.

617
00:36:01,320 --> 00:36:03,120
Do you still remember what you said

618
00:36:03,200 --> 00:36:04,840
when we competed with Di Liu High School?

619
00:36:05,640 --> 00:36:06,720
You said that

620
00:36:06,800 --> 00:36:09,040
you will defeat the opponent
in your own way.

621
00:36:09,480 --> 00:36:10,600
That is your tennis.

622
00:36:12,040 --> 00:36:13,240
I am the same.

623
00:36:13,840 --> 00:36:16,040
I don't want you to give up your
data-based tennis.

624
00:36:16,640 --> 00:36:18,600
Just like I won't give up
my way of playing tennis

625
00:36:18,680 --> 00:36:20,120
because of your words.

626
00:36:21,240 --> 00:36:23,760
You taught me to be flexible right?

627
