The training amount today is not done.

628
00:36:30,480 --> 00:36:31,640
I will run back home.

629
00:36:33,480 --> 00:36:35,280
Don't be restrained by your data,

630
00:36:35,360 --> 00:36:36,400
Zhiming.

631
