637
00:37:20,640 --> 00:37:23,160
It brought lots of pressure to you.

638
00:37:24,080 --> 00:37:25,360
I don't blame it on you.

639
00:37:25,440 --> 00:37:27,240
Of course, you can't blame it on me.

640
00:37:27,480 --> 00:37:28,320
[soft chuckle]

641
00:37:28,400 --> 00:37:32,000
Because I have considered carefully
for the next competitions.

642
00:37:32,080 --> 00:37:33,960
[Tang Jiale] Do you want to listen
to my ideas?

643
00:37:34,400 --> 00:37:35,240
Yes.

644
00:37:35,360 --> 00:37:37,600
In fact, Yue Yang in Xing Yao

645
00:37:37,680 --> 00:37:39,880
is the same type of player like us.

646
00:37:40,200 --> 00:37:42,080
[Tang Jiale] The only thing
is they will first...

647
00:37:42,160 --> 00:37:44,200
[Dayong] The help I can offer Jiale
is less and less.

648
00:37:45,480 --> 00:37:46,760
In fact, if I were not here,

649
00:37:47,440 --> 00:37:48,640
he would be strong as well.

650
00:37:50,960 --> 00:37:53,320
[jingling]

651
00:38:05,920 --> 00:38:06,760
Dad.

652
00:38:08,880 --> 00:38:10,080
Come and play tennis with me.

653
00:38:10,800 --> 00:38:11,800
You don't have to play

654
00:38:11,880 --> 00:38:13,440
in the match with Xing Yao do you?

655
00:38:14,400 --> 00:38:15,400
Come and play with me.

656
00:38:15,480 --> 00:38:16,760
Since you don't have to play

657
00:38:16,840 --> 00:38:18,640
I don't have to play with you right?

658
00:38:19,480 --> 00:38:20,440
Come.

659
00:38:20,520 --> 00:38:21,360
Hey.

660
00:38:21,440 --> 00:38:22,760
It hurts.

661
00:38:24,040 --> 00:38:25,840
I really want to play with you.

662
00:38:25,920 --> 00:38:28,400
But don't think the wound
in my little finger is a minor injury.

663
00:38:28,480 --> 00:38:30,440
